These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, singing, skydiving, board-games
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, july, october
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, aristoff, fonseca, cain
City: prague, london, edinburgh, miami
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Hobby    | skydiving   | singing       | hiking | board-games   |
| Birthday        | december    | october  | july      | january |
| Cigar         | cain      | aristoff | fonseca         | oliveros   |
| City   | prague | london       | edinburgh        | miami   |

