.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
City: boston, london, edinburgh, hamburg
House: gothic-revival, modern, art-deco, colonial
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pepper, nectarine, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, gardening, traveling
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
2. the person traveling to london is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to boston is between the modern house and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person eating cherry is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
9. the modern house is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| City           | london | boston | hamburg | edinburgh |
| House   | gothic-revival  | art-deco | modern         | colonial      |
| Food         | nectarine      | pepper    | cherry         | grapes   |
| Hobby     | video-games         | photography    | traveling          | gardening         |

