.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, adventure, crime, mystery
House: modern, townhouse, colonial, ranch-style
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, august, june, october
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, billiard, mah-jongg
 1. the colonial house is the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 7. the modern house is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person playing billiard and the townhouse house##2
 9. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | adventure | mystery  | horror | crime      |
| House   | modern       | ranch-style    | townhouse      | colonial      |
| Birthday           | october     | september     | august         | june   |
| Game         | billiard | poker | bridge     | mah-jongg |

