7. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person eating blueberry and the person who likes apricot##2
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
