 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the cottage house##1
10. the owner of the ferret is between the person who growstulip and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
