The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, trance, disco, hip-hop
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, magic-tricks, drawing, collecting
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the bike##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the fan of trance##1
11. the fan of disco is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |     4     |
| Transport      | bike      | snowmobile  | trike | helicopter      |
| Pet   | pony       | guinea-pig   | horse    | hedgehog    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | trance | reggae      | disco |
