4 different pets are kept: horse, goat, fish, cat
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, canadian, egyptian, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, emerald, lilac, chestnut
 1. the malaysian is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the owner of the horse is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is the malaysian##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the canadian##3
11. the owner of the cat is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Game         | billiard      | snooker | whist       | monopoly   |
| Pet   | cat     | goat | fish | horse |
| Nationality   | dutch    | canadian     | egyptian        | malaysian       |
| Color     | lilac | emerald   | blood-red   | chestnut       |

