.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, white, green, blue
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, malaysian, dutch
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, frog, ferret
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, dubstep, classical, house
 1. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
 2. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the argentine##1
 3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the egyptian is between the fan of classical and the fan of dubstep##2
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is between the egyptian and the fan of jazz##2
 7. the owner of the frog is the dutch##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the person who likes green is the egyptian##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Color          | white | blue   | green   | purple |
| Nationality           | argentine   | malaysian     | egyptian   | dutch |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | goldfish    | ferret   | frog   |
| Music-Genre         | jazz    | dubstep | house | classical    |

 